Targeting the Endocannabinoid System: From the Need for New Therapies to the 
Development of a Promising Strategy. What About Pancreatic Cancer?

Garmpis N(#)(1)(2), Damaskos C(#)(3)(4), Dimitroulis D(#)(1), Garmpi A(#)(5), 
Diamantis E(6), Sarantis P(7), Georgakopoulou VE(8), Patsouras A(9), Prevezanos 
