C(7), Papalexis P(5)(12), Antoniou EA(1)(2), Kontzoglou K(1)(2), Kouraklis 
G(13).

Author information:
(1)Second Department of Propedeutic Surgery, Laiko General Hospital, Medical 
School, National and Kapodistrian University of Athens, Athens, Greece.
(2)N.S. Christeas Laboratory of Experimental Surgery and Surgical Research, 
Medical School, National and Kapodistrian University of Athens, Athens, Greece.
(3)N.S. Christeas Laboratory of Experimental Surgery and Surgical Research, 
Medical School, National and Kapodistrian University of Athens, Athens, Greece; 
x_damaskos@yahoo.gr.
(4)Renal Transplantation Unit, Laiko General Hospital, Athens, Greece.
(5)First Department of Propedeutic Internal Medicine, Laiko General Hospital, 
